These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
City: prague, liverpool, nizza, colone
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person eating mango is the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| City   | liverpool  | prague     | nizza   | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
House: palace, townhouse, futuristic, farmhouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the palace house is on the far right##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse | townhouse | palace    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, canadian, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the colombian is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the russian##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality         | colombian | russian | canadian   | japanese |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
City: boston, nizza, san-francisco, berlin
1. the person traveling to nizza is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| City         | nizza | berlin   | san-francisco | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski, tram, subway
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Transport   | subway | tram | jet-ski | taxi |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

