The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | satire | mystery      | disaster | horror |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

