3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Pet    | goldfish | guinea-pig  | hamster | dog |
