.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
4 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, mouse, pony
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Pet   | frog  | mouse | pony           | lizard   |

