4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | bongani      | cain | ritmeester | chaman |
| Transport     | quad-bike | van    | subway  | roller |

