.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, emerald, light-blue, green
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee   | soy-milk | cola   | fanta      |
| Color   | white | green      | emerald | light-blue |

