.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, frog, pony
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Pet     | frog  | rabbit    | guinea-pig       | pony |

 